Narok County happened after a heavy downpour that destroyed houses and farms. The two children were buried alive while sleeping. A search and rescue mission to find the children was
hampered by impassable roads. The bodies were recovered in the afternoon. Kenya's annual long rains have brought heavy flooding
around the country, displacing thousands of people. The Red Cross says 41 people have died from floods in
